{"tid":734593,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 偏多字遊記 ] 紅磡往哈爾濱的火車旅程","createTime":"2018-07-08T18:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T07:46:29.000Z","uid":191832,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c5db3bbf14db26be7fe4570e883dd1751acd9f","tid":734593,"uid":191832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我參加咗個哈爾濱 + 海參崴 7 天團 <br />\n但係 7 日嘅旅行對一個放緊 sem break 嘅廢青嚟講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又好似有啲短<br />\n所以不如試下坐火車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便去下其他城市 <del>其實得 3 個</del><br />\n所以就係咁開始咗我嘅硬臥之旅<br />\n冇錯 係硬臥<br />\n哪有錢你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>- 行程 -</strong><br />\nDay 1 九龍 (紅磡) 出發<br />\nDay 2 - 3 上海<br />\nDay 4 - 5 天津<br />\nDay 6 - 8 哈爾濱<br />\nDay 9 - 12 俄羅斯 (海參崴)<br />\nDay 13 哈爾濱<br />\nDay 14 - 16 大連<br />\nDay 17 已經返咗香港啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實本身有諗過經北京去<br />\n咁樣會再平啲<br />\n但係京九 / 滬九直通車係隔日開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如七月咁 <br />\n去北京 Z98 就開單日 1 3 5<br />\n上海 Z100 就開雙日 2 4 6<br />\n而每個月都會調轉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就唔到時間嘅關係<br />\n就揀咗 Z100 <br />\n晏晝 15:15 由紅磡出發<br />\n搭到第二日 10:37 到上海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時係紅磡搭西鐵就搭得多<br />\n直通車都係第一次搭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/220523_9a0552f3f0e793ced30056e505584cab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F220523_9a0552f3f0e793ced30056e505584cab.jpg&h=d3ed5666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一上車就聞到有陣煙味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係完全冇諗過<br />\n後尾先知原來中國啲綠皮車 車廂與車廂之間<br />\n係可以食煙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n硬臥嘅間格係一開六<br />\n即係一格入面有兩邊上中下鋪<br />\n冇門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而一卡入面大隔都有 11 格到<br />\n可想而知其實都有啲逼<br />\n<br />\n而訓落去感覺同 hall 張床差唔多<br />\n不過中鋪同上鋪嘅空間真係好細 <br />\n最多都係攤係到<br />\n坐都坐唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以價錢都係下鋪最貴<br />\n差幾蚊至十幾蚊不等<br />\n不過鍾意睇風景嘅我會揀中鋪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然下鋪都睇到<br />\n不過我唔鍾意人坐我張床咁<br />\n<br />\n開車冇耐就會有乘務員同你換臥鋪卡<br />\n基本上呢個係中國臥鋪火車必備嘅環節 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即使呢架車中途不停站 (誤?)<br />\n<br />\n搭咗兩個鐘大概 5 點 3 到就嚟到廣州東<br />\n話不停站其實係呃人嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺廣州東佢會拖多幾卡車<br />\n令程車冇咁蝕<br />\n順帶一提 因為未入境嘅關係<br />\n所以中途停嘅站都唔可以落車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁晚飯點算? <br />\n有得揀嘅<br />\n佢有專人行勻晒咁多車卡賣飯盒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢就廿幾蚊人仔<br />\n另外仲有熱水爐俾你沖杯麵<br />\n不過一場嚟到 就梗係試下餐車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n餐車係第 12 卡<br />\n而我係第 6 卡<br />\n換句話說要穿過軟臥同高包嘅車卡先去到<br />\n呢下先見識到咩叫一分錢一分貨<br />\n有錢係啲野係豪華啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過唔好以為餐車時時都會有野食<br />\n佢有固定嘅供餐時間<br />\n而且太晏去啲野係會賣晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚餐係 6 點鐘開始<br />\n而架車仲係廣州東<br />\n無錯 佢仲未開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廣州東嘅開車時間係 18:12<br />\n差唔多停成粒鐘<br />\n<br />\n餸菜方面都係上海菜為主<br />\n印象中有燻魚 炒菜咁 <br />\n嗌咗甜酸骨同蛋餅<br />\n味道一般 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊蛋好多油<br />\n碟甜酸骨都冇乜肉<br />\n最多係汁<br />\n價錢就兩個人食左七十幾蚊<br />\n所以我會話志在食風景 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/003818_6b849cdebe4fbd518a40d714d7e58fdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F003818_6b849cdebe4fbd518a40d714d7e58fdc.jpg&h=2d4fed87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個床位都會有閱讀燈<br />\n就算夜晚熄咗車廂燈都可以繼續做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而呢個車卡入面有裝設有限度嘅雙腳插頭<br />\n可以俾你叉下電<br />\n不過前提係你可能要同你爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似 2 - 3 格床先有一個插頭<br />\n<br />\n去到凌晨 1 點嘅時候<br />\n就停第二個站 - 株洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上成架車都黑晒<br />\n所以醒咗陣就繼續訓<br />\n<br />\n車卡入面係有洗臉間<br />\n有塊大鏡同幾個洗手盤<br />\n雖然唔知佢啲水乾唔乾淨<br />\n不過都用咗嚟刷牙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n餐車嘅早餐時間係 7 點幾<br />\n唔食餐車都仲有 白粥 炒麵 嘅飯盒可以揀<br />\n盛惠 15 蚊人仔<br />\n而我就食左餐車嘅素肉蛋麵<br />\n不過都幾油下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢餐牌到仲有 &quot; 西式早餐 &quot;<br />\n就係方包加果醬送隻蛋同咖啡<br />\n明顯唔吸引 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再過多三個鐘到就嚟到上海 <br />\n架車係准點 10:37 到<br />\n都有啲 surprise <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過整體嚟講<br />\n滬九直通車都算係最舒服果程 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然都坐咗 19 個鐘<br />\n但係唔算好多人坐<br />\n都幾多吉床<br />\n搭嘅人多數都係老人家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就講下啲快閃行程<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思個 post 冇乜圖<br />\n唔係影咗好多相"},{"pid":"3de079b107185d766a4b46f9a655f04620242627","tid":734593,"uid":79206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:08:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5daf14a96d739eab792ff56b58b6577cc89c8c06","tid":734593,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"都幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533ce8f2a37ea7b0428965882da3da0379189b03","tid":734593,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"edbe5cf41f19d9e3695964c9af1a57ff9bc1def5","tid":734593,"uid":74076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:25:03.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"32992c0b639bc176c6078d91b9358f8973682644","tid":734593,"uid":146076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:27:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"a2cc1d6cb032a111aad2bc9f0fc031495ef5e65f","tid":734593,"uid":86985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"00c9874a90dc3c3efc104c6493178b4275e0345e","tid":734593,"uid":10604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:32:12.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2e45973057971cadf2f6563f4f97d0eec53220a0","tid":734593,"uid":12328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:37:27.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"5cdea188c8bb080a88fac3d20f4c3ca862002f3d","tid":734593,"uid":156405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油 巴打"},{"pid":"841838e93bcfde41093073831237b25ccf3501d5","tid":734593,"uid":96411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"f48a2f6e628d4fc4d12b42fae0fe429a8f7183a5","tid":734593,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:36:13.000Z","msg":"旅行圑點搵？"},{"pid":"512c69f1c1a6592b60666331a72b790947fef876","tid":734593,"uid":19949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"廣州東始發嘅K98/97,K100/99係日日開<br />\n所以果日有九龍始發車就加埋大陸卡先開<br />\n果日香港車係去第二度就自己開"},{"pid":"86776aa05835c7f313e68509e6a051f6b6e1a838","tid":734593,"uid":12328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"樓主火車出軌？"},{"pid":"6b4fe33e9ef6e52701dcd5f04d25b4b2b976e493","tid":734593,"uid":33777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86776aa05835c7f313e68509e6a051f6b6e1a838","tid":734593,"uid":12328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"樓主火車出軌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e906f6963962bae2393839d43369c7fd01114d41","tid":734593,"uid":234461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86776aa05835c7f313e68509e6a051f6b6e1a838","tid":734593,"uid":12328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"樓主火車出軌？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"真係出咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20b8067ab599bf740205ce4155c87545b634612","tid":734593,"uid":12328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e906f6963962bae2393839d43369c7fd01114d41","tid":734593,"uid":234461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86776aa05835c7f313e68509e6a051f6b6e1a838","tid":734593,"uid":12328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"樓主火車出軌？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"真係出咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}